---
title: Chicken Chow Mein-Style Noodles with Stir-Fried Veggies and Peanuts
description: Savoury with a touch of sweetness, this dish combines tender-crisp veggies with irresistibly flavourful noodles! A final sprinkle of crunchy peanuts gives this dinner 10s across the board!
